backend:
    pip install django
    django start project < project_name . >

    python manage.py startapp  <app_name>

    register app in project settings.py under INSTALLED_APPS


URL and Routing configurations
create url.py file (used to connect the views to your urls )
create url and view (see hello world sample)
include app url in project urls

install djangorestframework. 
https://www.django-rest-framework.org/#installation

add rest_framework to installed apps in project setting

https://www.django-rest-framework.org/api-guide/views/#function-based-views
import into views.py - from rest_framework.decorators import api_view
import Response as well ---
from rest_framework.response import Response
